  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200&deg;C/ 180&deg;C (fan)/ 400&deg;F/ Gas 6</p>\r\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Peel and chop the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;finely</p>\r\n<p>Peel and chop the <strong>brown&nbsp;onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;finely&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/781.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/781.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/781.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/781.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/781.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a matching lid, with a drizzle of&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong>&nbsp;over a medium-high&nbsp;heat&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped</strong>&nbsp;<strong>onion</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>chopped carrot</strong>,&nbsp;a generous pinch of&nbsp;<strong>salt</strong>&nbsp;and cook for 5-8 min or until&nbsp;softened</p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>chicken&nbsp;stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span>&nbsp;</strong>in 300ml&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span>&nbsp;<strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/781.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/781.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/781.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/781.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
