      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add 30g <span class=\"text-danger\">[60g]</span>&nbsp;<strong>butter</strong> to a pot over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p>Once melted, add 30g <span class=\"text-danger\">[60g]</span>&nbsp;<strong>flour</strong> and stir for 2-3 min until a sandy coloured paste is formed &ndash; this is your <strong>roux</strong></p>",
